<i>♪ In the heat of the night ♪</i>

03:16.656 --> 03:19.200
Where you keepin' the pie tonight?

03:20.827 --> 03:23.371
Man ate the last piece
just before you come in.

03:29.252 --> 03:31.921
Well, what's that little ol' orphan
sittin' right up there?

03:33.882 --> 03:36.009
Marble cake.

03:39.387 --> 03:40.930
Tell you what, Sam.

03:41.014 --> 03:45.059
Bein' she's in there by her little ol' lonesome,
I'll let ya have her for free.

03:45.143 --> 03:47.812
I told you 'bout that "Sam" business,
didn't I? Huh?

03:48.897 --> 03:50.315
I'm sorry, Mr. Wood.

03:50.398 --> 03:53.109
I mean, uh, Officer Wood.

04:40.406 --> 04:43.326
<i>♪ Well, a bowlegged Polly
And a knock-kneed Paul ♪</i>

04:43.409 --> 04:46.079
<i>♪ A bowlegged Polly
