04:46.162 --> 04:48.581
<i>♪ A bowlegged Polly and a knock-kneed Paul ♪</i>

04:48.665 --> 04:50.500
<i>♪ They can't get together at all ♪</i>

04:50.583 --> 04:53.628
<i>♪ Just like the worm in the cornfield
Said to his brother ♪</i>

04:53.711 --> 04:56.631
<i>♪ Yeah, go in one ear and out the other ♪</i>

05:09.310 --> 05:12.522
<i>♪ Well, a bucktoothed Clara
And a cross-eyed Clyde ♪</i>

05:12.605 --> 05:14.816
<i>♪ A bucktoothed Clara
And a cross-eyed Clyde ♪</i>

05:14.899 --> 05:17.652
<i>♪ Like ol' bowlegged Polly
And a knock-kneed Paul ♪</i>

